## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="4f349-104">屬性或欄位必須是公用的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4f349-104">The property or field must be public.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4f349-105">包含屬性的類別都必須標記為<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementEntityAttribute>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4f349-105">The class that contains the property must be marked with the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementEntityAttribute> attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4f349-106">將不會檢測任何欄位或類別中未標示有這個或其他 WMI 提供者擴充功能屬性的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4f349-106">Any fields or properties in the class that are not marked with this or another WMI Provider Extensions attribute will not be instrumented.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="4f349-107">下列範例會示範如何使用 ManagementProbe 屬性來指出欄位代表唯讀的 WMI 屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4f349-107">The following example shows how to use the ManagementProbe attribute to indicate that a field represents a read-only WMI property.</span></span>  

```csharp  
[ManagementProbe]  
string count;  
```  

 <span data-ttu-id="4f349-108">下一個範例示範如何使用 ManagementProbe 屬性標記的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4f349-108">The next example shows how to use the ManagementProbe attribute to mark a property.</span></span>  

```csharp  
// Use the ManagementProbe attribute to specify that a property  
// is a read-only property in the provider. Consumers will be  
// able to get this property value through WMI.  
[ManagementProbe]  
public int ReadOnlyProperty  
{  
    get { return this.propertyValue; }  
}  
```
